attributes.PROJECT_FICHE_SHORT_TITLE: EE, LV, LT synchronisation with CEN
attributes.PROJECT_FULL_TITLE: Further infrastructure aspects related to the implementation of the synchronisation of the Baltic States system with the continental European network
attributes.TECHNICAL_DESCR:
This generic project shall implement the first phase of improvements in system control and stability required for synchronous operation with Continental Europe:

- Development of Baltic AGC and frequency stability assessment systems with special protection schemes,

-Upgrades of SCADAs and other IT systems and their environment needed for real time operation and planning,

- Upgrades to HVDC connectors EstLink 1, EstLink 2 and Nordbalt, etc,

- Construction of three synchronous condensers in Püssi (Estonia), Ventspils (Latvia) and Alytus (Lithuania),

- Battery Energy Storage System for Latvian power system.
attributes.PROMOTERS: Augstsprieguma tikls AS (LV) ; Elering AS (EE) ; LITGRID AB (LT)
